独立开发商取消了“Inkbound”中的所有货币化以同意“玩家情绪” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/indie-developer-removing-all-monetization-in-inkbound-to-agree-with-player-sentiment-3515774?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=indie-开发者删除了 inkbound 中的所有货币化以同意玩家情绪Imogen DonovanMon, 16 Oct 2023 12:17:51 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3515774 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “很明显，行业和玩家的情绪正在与这些功能的存在背道而驰”</p><p>这位<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/indie-developer-removing-all-monetisation-in-inkbound-to-agree-with-player-sentiment-3515774">独立开发者取消了“Inkbound”中的所有货币化以同意“玩家情绪”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>奇幻 Roguelike <em>Inkbound</em>的开发商 Shiny Shoe 宣布将从游戏中删除所有形式的游戏内货币化内容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-mountain-goats-john-darnielle-talks-magic-the-gathering-secret-lair-set-3483851">山羊乐队的约翰·达尼尔 (John Darnielle) 谈论为《万智牌》写预言</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1062810/view/7306585773982973654?snr=1_5_9_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">游戏的 Steam 列表中发表的一篇文章</a>中，该团队辩称，最初将货币化纳入升级通行证和化妆品商店是为了支持游戏的开发。</p><p>此外，他们的目标是确保微交易“100％可选，仅用于装饰，对游戏玩法没有影响，并且没有 FOMO”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3515790" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3515790" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3515790" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3515790" class="wp-caption-text">一个人在游戏电脑上玩游戏 图片来源：Ella Don，来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>然而，该公司表示，游戏行业的现状让 Shiny Shoe 得出结论，货币化并不是为游戏进展提供资金的流行方式。</p><p> “但是，很明显，行业和玩家的情绪正在与这些功能的存在背道而驰。因此，我们将完全取消游戏内的货币化，”该帖子继续说道。</p><p> “对于所有阅读本文并在游戏中购买过任何东西的人来说，真的谢谢你们。我们希望到目前为止您在<em>Inkbound</em>中度过了愉快的时光，我们将尽力在明年某个时候发布强大的 1.0。</p><p> “作为此次过渡的一部分，任何进行过购买的人都将获得额外的奖金奖励，以感谢您的支持。” </p><figure id="attachment_3515792" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3515792" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3515792" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3515792" class="wp-caption-text">游戏电脑 图片来源：Ella Don via Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>因此，升级通行证中的内容将通过“Steam 上出售的仅限外观的可选“支持者包”DLC”提供。任何拥有《故事开始》或《恐怖星舰》高级通行证的人都将获得这些曲目中所有无人认领的奖励。</p><p>其余的化妆品内容和货币将在<em>Inkbound</em>中找到并通过玩来解锁。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，《龙之<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/like-a-dragon-gaiden-will-add-english-dub-after-launch-3515571"><em>龙外传：抹去名字的男人》</em>将于 11 月 9 日发售时，不会包含英文配音</a>。</p><p>这位<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/indie-developer-removing-all-monetisation-in-inkbound-to-agree-with-player-sentiment-3515774">独立开发者取消了“Inkbound”中的所有货币化以同意“玩家情绪”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《三人行》主演苏珊娜·萨默斯去世，享年 76 岁https://www.nme.com/news/tv/thirds-company-star-suzanne-somers-dies-ged-76-3515804?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=thirds-company-star-suzanne-somers-dies- 76岁Adam StarkeyMon, 16 Oct 2023 12:17:48 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3515804 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="苏珊·萨默斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位演员还在《步步惊心》中扮演卡罗尔·福斯特-兰伯特</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/threes-company-star-suzanne-somers-dies-aged-76-3515804">《三人行》主演苏珊娜·萨默斯去世，享年 76</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">岁</a></p>; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="苏珊·萨默斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Suzanne-Somers-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>因出演情景喜剧<em>《Three&#39;s Company》</em>和<em>《Step By Step》</em>而闻名的苏珊娜·萨默斯 (Suzanne Somers) 去世，享年 76 岁。</p><p>正如她的家人在 Instagram 上发表的声明所证实的那样，这位演员于周日早上（10 月 15 日）因与乳腺癌作斗争而去世。</p><p>声明中写道：“苏珊娜·萨默斯于 10 月 15 日凌晨在家中平静地去世。” “她在侵袭性乳腺癌中存活了 23 年多。</p><p> “苏珊娜周围都是她慈爱的丈夫艾伦、儿子布鲁斯和她的直系亲属。 10 月 16 日，她的家人聚集在一起庆祝她的 77 岁生日。相反，他们将庆祝她非凡的一生，并感谢她数百万深爱她的粉丝和追随者。”</p><p>据 <a href="https://people.com/suzanne-somers-dead-at-76-8358227" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》报道</em></a>，私人家庭葬礼将于下周举行，追悼会定于 11 月举行。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CycJ-orpQEn/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.8